    "name": "Kritter: Defend Together",
    "steam_appid": 2103950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，小玩意儿们！我是方舟任务 182，或者亲切点叫我 M.ark。你们最爱的时空飞船！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赶紧简单汇报一下：你们是我的 Kritters，M.ark 制造的防御机器人，我需要你们。在一次不幸的事故（绝对不是在消耗了乙醇煤油之后发生的）之后，我可怜地坠毁在这个完全未知的星球上。问题是？我丢失了大部分必要的导航零件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/471fc6cb5f9673e1d15dd6f45392d342.poster.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/471fc6cb5f9673e1d15dd6f45392d342.webm?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/471fc6cb5f9673e1d15dd6f45392d342.mp4?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们的角色是？</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这个星球，找到所有对我们逃脱有用的资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护我免受所有可能损坏我华丽机身的外界威胁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变得更强，然后带着我们离开这里！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我想我已经说得很清楚了，但鉴于你们看起来像一群笨手笨脚的家伙，我以防万一提醒你们：我拥有时间回溯选项。如果我感到受到威胁……噗，小小的回到过去，你们就得回去再干掉那些该死的怪物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好处是，凭借你们前几次尝试的经验和资源，你们可以在下一次游戏中变得更强。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/b0b8f8d0f05ba2b17d73bd50335c273e.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在我被编程时，我配备了一份在极端紧急情况下使用的《生存手册》。它上面写着：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“启动 Kritter 程序……” 这已经完成了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“祈祷和哭泣……” 好吧，这部分不太有趣……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >啊哈！“派 Kritters 去探索周围环境，并回收构建防御工事所需的矿物和神器。” 这就更有用了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/1d365f4d9a8c952053d3a8692d1ab22f.poster.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/1d365f4d9a8c952053d3a8692d1ab22f.webm?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/1d365f4d9a8c952053d3a8692d1ab22f.mp4?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据《手册》，我们将需要资源来制造城墙、炮塔和陷阱，以方便我们生存。它还建议保持警惕，因为在探索过程中可能会发生某些事件：竞技场战斗、包含升级宝箱的基地、提供金币和资源的巡逻队……嗯，这份《手册》知道的还真不少！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/280481c4ae8352486faf21100364383e.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《手册》还说：“你的探索时间有限。你必须在计时结束前回到 M.ark 附近，保护它免受试图摧毁它的敌波侵袭，并准备好你的防御。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它甚至知道我的名字！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/c017a9d331f442cdfa8eba9014464fdf.poster.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/c017a9d331f442cdfa8eba9014464fdf.webm?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/c017a9d331f442cdfa8eba9014464fdf.mp4?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看来我们面对的波次越多，敌人就会越多，而且会越强大，甚至可能包括迷你 Boss。因此，建议在所有战线上合理分配工作，并确保敌人不会到达 M.ark（就是我）。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/18402c26be2f9644fdeba0bca6c33f90.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/ebcfb697b2ac217f65544bc4efe4f013.webp?t=1771948283\" width=123 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谢谢你的提醒，手册……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一波之间，你将有多种奖励选择，无论是质量还是效果，都能让你变得更强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/f74a64efcba8b7c04251ff642c247b5e.poster.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/f74a64efcba8b7c04251ff642c247b5e.webm?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/f74a64efcba8b7c04251ff642c247b5e.mp4?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这也是你们的小小的咖啡休息时间：你们可以升级和强化防御，以及与一位准备“用自己的创造者换取一些硬币”的商人聊天。他主要出售升级……有意思！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/a57fd46a30479b774b785ea524e1e06a.webp?t=1771948283\" width=137 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“方舟 182 型号的时间回溯过程将启动。” 我已经告诉过你们了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，我们将带着我们的记忆和最重要的资源被送回过去，特别是那些能够“以指数级和永久性方式改进方舟 182 型号及其 Kritters 能力”的资源，这与在游戏过程中获得的临时升级不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/7453f6bd68f1dbc2b8411f759f22d343.poster.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/7453f6bd68f1dbc2b8411f759f22d343.webm?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/7453f6bd68f1dbc2b8411f759f22d343.mp4?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kritters 也有可能更换型号，包括：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>防御者：</strong> 近战专家，更坚固。用你的剑做出漂亮的风车旋转，把你的敌人变成萨拉米香肠。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>工程师：</strong> 想来点外星烧烤吗？凭借他的火焰喷射器和炮塔，他是造成区域伤害和覆盖多条战线的完美选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>追踪者：</strong> 远程 Kritter，擅长爆炸物和精准射击！这里埋个小地雷，那里来一发导弹，然后，搞定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>忍者：</strong> 迅捷锋利，绝不手软。他比同伴更快，通过冲刺穿过敌人并将其撕裂，同时从远处投下苦无雨。简单、干脆、致命。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多即将推出……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/867f3c0610e20e1120fa10daef5982bd.poster.avif?t=1771948283\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/867f3c0610e20e1120fa10daef5982bd.webm?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103950/extras/867f3c0610e20e1120fa10daef5982bd.mp4?t=1771948283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《手册》到此为止。它似乎没有指示其他步骤……尽管如此，它向我们表达了“最诚挚的哀悼”，并将“向你们的家人报告你和 Kritters 的损失”。它真好心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗，Kritters？ <strong>各就各位！</strong></p>",
